Text.SourceString: Morning, hun. Made us some breakfast!
Text.LocalizedString: Morning, hun. Made us some breakfast!

Text.SourceString: Whipped up a little something special for you, hun.//I hope you like it!
Text.LocalizedString: Whipped up a little something special for you, hun.//I hope you like it!

Text.SourceString: So, what's on your agenda today, <PlayerName>$Player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: So, what's on your agenda today, <PlayerName>$Player</>?

Text.SourceString: There's something so calming about this place...so peaceful.
Text.LocalizedString: There's something so calming about this place...so peaceful.

Text.SourceString: How's your day, hun? I want to hear all about it!
Text.LocalizedString: How's your day, hun? I want to hear all about it!

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking of getting cozy with a book and heading to bed soon, hun. Are you going to join me?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking of getting cozy with a book and heading to bed soon, hun. Are you going to join me?

Text.SourceString: I'll see if I can stop by the beach shack today. I'm thinking of making some lobster for dinner. Yeah?
Text.LocalizedString: I'll see if I can stop by the beach shack today. I'm thinking of making some lobster for dinner. Yeah?

Text.SourceString: Uh-oh, I might have unintentionally swapped <NpcName>Charles</>' patients' files with mine. Whoopsie!
Text.LocalizedString: Uh-oh, I might have unintentionally swapped <NpcName>Charles</>' patients' files with mine. Whoopsie!

Text.SourceString: I'm not supposed to bring them home, but I'm a little late on documentation, so...
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not supposed to bring them home, but I'm a little late on documentation, so...

Text.SourceString: It's raining outside. Should we cuddle up, hun?
Text.LocalizedString: It's raining outside. Should we cuddle up, hun?

Text.SourceString: It's snowing outside. How about we take advantage of this weather and stay in bed all day?
Text.LocalizedString: It's snowing outside. How about we take advantage of this weather and stay in bed all day?

Text.SourceString: It's raining super hard today.//I hope our farm is okay. Be careful out there, hun.
Text.LocalizedString: It's raining super hard today.//I hope our farm is okay. Be careful out there, hun.

Text.SourceString: I tried my hand at tidying up the house today, but not sure if you can tell.
Text.LocalizedString: I tried my hand at tidying up the house today, but not sure if you can tell.

Text.SourceString: I ran into <NpcName>Millie</> on the way here, and he asked if I could hang out with her sometime.//<portrait=concerned>Yeah, maybe... I'm usually so worn out after work, you know.
Text.LocalizedString: I ran into <NpcName>Millie</> on the way here, and he asked if I could hang out with her sometime.//<portrait=concerned>Yeah, maybe... I'm usually so worn out after work, you know.

Text.SourceString: Is everything alright at home, hun?
Text.LocalizedString: Is everything alright at home, hun?

Text.SourceString: I have to help <NpcName>Charles</> with some inventory, or as he calls it, 'doing my job.' Haha!
Text.LocalizedString: I have to help <NpcName>Charles</> with some inventory, or as he calls it, 'doing my job.' Haha!

Text.SourceString: Our water dispenser at the clinic broke the other day. Good thing I knew how to fix it.//<NpcName>Charles</> was helpless and didn't drink anything until I came to the clinic.
Text.LocalizedString: Our water dispenser at the clinic broke the other day. Good thing I knew how to fix it.//<NpcName>Charles</> was helpless and didn't drink anything until I came to the clinic.

Text.SourceString: I thought I came into work today.//Yep, I have my lunch with me. Don't worry, hun.
Text.LocalizedString: I thought I came into work today.//Yep, I have my lunch with me. Don't worry, hun.

Text.SourceString: Just being here, watching you do your farming thing, makes me happy.
Text.LocalizedString: Just being here, watching you do your farming thing, makes me happy.

Text.SourceString: The clinic's usually dead at this hour, so I'm just gonna hang here and chill.//<NpcName>Charles</> can handle it, no sweat.
Text.LocalizedString: The clinic's usually dead at this hour, so I'm just gonna hang here and chill.//<NpcName>Charles</> can handle it, no sweat.

Text.SourceString: I like spending time with you here, hun.
Text.LocalizedString: I like spending time with you here, hun.

Text.SourceString: Gosh, the weather today is great. Couldn't ask for a better day to soak in the sun.
Text.LocalizedString: Gosh, the weather today is great. Couldn't ask for a better day to soak in the sun.

Text.SourceString: You look amazing today, hun... Wow! I'm the luckiest girl in the world!
Text.LocalizedString: You look amazing today, hun... Wow! I'm the luckiest girl in the world!

Text.SourceString: I love you, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Please don't ever forget that.
Text.LocalizedString: I love you, <PlayerName>$Player</>. Please don't ever forget that.

Text.SourceString: Out of everyone in my life, you are the most important person to me, hun.
Text.LocalizedString: Out of everyone in my life, you are the most important person to me, hun.

Text.SourceString: Hun, I'm going to head to the Cherry Blossom Festival early tomorrow for my doctor duties.//I'll see you there?
Text.LocalizedString: Hun, I'm going to head to the Cherry Blossom Festival early tomorrow for my doctor duties.//I'll see you there?

Text.SourceString: For the Harvest Festival tomorrow, I promised <NpcName>Charles</> I'd be the official doctor in charge, so I'll need to get there bright and early.
Text.LocalizedString: For the Harvest Festival tomorrow, I promised <NpcName>Charles</> I'd be the official doctor in charge, so I'll need to get there bright and early.

Text.SourceString: I'll just see you in Alun-Alun, okay?
Text.LocalizedString: I'll just see you in Alun-Alun, okay?

Text.SourceString: Should we bring anything to <NpcName>Bree</>'s dinner tomorrow, hun?
Text.LocalizedString: Should we bring anything to <NpcName>Bree</>'s dinner tomorrow, hun?

Text.SourceString: I feel bad never bringing anything...but is it rude, uh, to bring anything though? I feel like it is rude.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel bad never bringing anything...but is it rude, uh, to bring anything though? I feel like it is rude.

Text.SourceString: I average around fourish hours a day at work when I'm at the Clinic…//During this time, I usually see patients, review medical histories, or check the inventory.//<NPCName>Charles</> runs the reception most of the time.
Text.LocalizedString: I average around fourish hours a day at work when I'm at the Clinic…//During this time, I usually see patients, review medical histories, or check the inventory.//<NPCName>Charles</> runs the reception most of the time.

Text.SourceString: It's awesome 'cause I hate handling reception.//Just sitting around up front? Ugh, so boring.
Text.LocalizedString: It's awesome 'cause I hate handling reception.//Just sitting around up front? Ugh, so boring.

Text.SourceString: Paying attention to what you eat is a great way to stay healthy in the long run.//Prevention is worth more than any cure.
Text.LocalizedString: Paying attention to what you eat is a great way to stay healthy in the long run.//Prevention is worth more than any cure.

Text.SourceString: Make sure to include fresh vegetables in your diet, hun.//They’re a great source of fiber and nutrients.
Text.LocalizedString: Make sure to include fresh vegetables in your diet, hun.//They’re a great source of fiber and nutrients.

Text.SourceString: I don't want you to get sick.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't want you to get sick.

Text.SourceString: Don't hesitate to shout if you ever have any questions about medicine or health.//<portrait=happy>Now that I'm your wife, you're my number one patient. V.I.P! He he!
Text.LocalizedString: Don't hesitate to shout if you ever have any questions about medicine or health.//<portrait=happy>Now that I'm your wife, you're my number one patient. V.I.P! He he!

Text.SourceString: Let me help put your mind at ease.
Text.LocalizedString: Let me help put your mind at ease.

Text.SourceString: Being in the sun is fine as long as you remember to wear sunscreen.
Text.LocalizedString: Being in the sun is fine as long as you remember to wear sunscreen.

Text.SourceString: Oh, another thing!//<portrait=normal>Remember to reapply sunscreen every few hours. That part’s important, and people always forget.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, another thing!//<portrait=normal>Remember to reapply sunscreen every few hours. That part’s important, and people always forget.

Text.SourceString: I should wear regular clothes more.//<portrait=normal>I’m too lazy to change after my shift, so I just go around in scrubs.
Text.LocalizedString: I should wear regular clothes more.//<portrait=normal>I’m too lazy to change after my shift, so I just go around in scrubs.

Text.SourceString: Chess is all about planning and strategy, just like health.//Well, for me, anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: Chess is all about planning and strategy, just like health.//Well, for me, anyway.

Text.SourceString: Heh, heh… You got me!//<portrait=normal>I do always find a way to bring the conversation back to health talk.
Text.LocalizedString: Heh, heh… You got me!//<portrait=normal>I do always find a way to bring the conversation back to health talk.

Text.SourceString: I don’t usually work on Fridays unless I have an appointment.//Or if there’s an emergency or something.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t usually work on Fridays unless I have an appointment.//Or if there’s an emergency or something.

Text.SourceString: I’m not too worried about it. The clinic’s usually very quiet.//<NPCName>Charles</> will do just fine on his own.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m not too worried about it. The clinic’s usually very quiet.//<NPCName>Charles</> will do just fine on his own.

Text.SourceString: Make sure to drink enough water, okay?//Our bodies need it.
Text.LocalizedString: Make sure to drink enough water, okay?//Our bodies need it.

Text.SourceString: It’s so easy to get carried away and forget to listen to our bodies.//I’m guilty of that too.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s so easy to get carried away and forget to listen to our bodies.//I’m guilty of that too.

Text.SourceString: One of the things I find most challenging about being a doctor is sometimes patients lie.//<portrait=normal>While it’s harmless in most cases, it’s always best to be honest with your doctor.
Text.LocalizedString: One of the things I find most challenging about being a doctor is sometimes patients lie.//<portrait=normal>While it’s harmless in most cases, it’s always best to be honest with your doctor.

Text.SourceString: It’s important for doctors to know your complete medical history to give you the best care possible.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s important for doctors to know your complete medical history to give you the best care possible.

Text.SourceString: I should totally rock a coat like <NPCName>Charles</> does.//<portrait=normal>Look at him, all sleek and stylish. That coat just adds a certain oomph, doesn't it?
Text.LocalizedString: I should totally rock a coat like <NPCName>Charles</> does.//<portrait=normal>Look at him, all sleek and stylish. That coat just adds a certain oomph, doesn't it?

Text.SourceString: But it’s just so hot and restricting.//And seriously, can't run a decent sprint with that coat flapping around like crazy.
Text.LocalizedString: But it’s just so hot and restricting.//And seriously, can't run a decent sprint with that coat flapping around like crazy.

Text.SourceString: Honestly, I'm so used to scrubs. Anything else feels weird and constricting, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: Honestly, I'm so used to scrubs. Anything else feels weird and constricting, you know?

Text.SourceString: I'm all about that simple life. As long as I've got a hot meal on the table, I consider it a good day.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm all about that simple life. As long as I've got a hot meal on the table, I consider it a good day.

Text.SourceString: Volleyball isn't exactly my forte yet, but hey, I won't turn down a game if someone asks.//Gotta keep the ball rolling!
Text.LocalizedString: Volleyball isn't exactly my forte yet, but hey, I won't turn down a game if someone asks.//Gotta keep the ball rolling!

Text.SourceString: Back in the day, I was part of this universal doctor program, traveling all over the world to help out.
Text.LocalizedString: Back in the day, I was part of this universal doctor program, traveling all over the world to help out.

Text.SourceString: The pay wasn’t good, but you get one heck of a lot of experience. Plus the satisfaction of helping people in need.
Text.LocalizedString: The pay wasn’t good, but you get one heck of a lot of experience. Plus the satisfaction of helping people in need.

Text.SourceString: Oh, and let me tell you, foreign travel really opens up your mind and toughens you up.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, and let me tell you, foreign travel really opens up your mind and toughens you up.

Text.SourceString: I try my best to live a healthy life, but some days it's harder than others, you know what I mean?
Text.LocalizedString: I try my best to live a healthy life, but some days it's harder than others, you know what I mean?

Text.SourceString: It wasn't easy for me to find someone I want to spend my life with.
Text.LocalizedString: It wasn't easy for me to find someone I want to spend my life with.

Text.SourceString: I'm so glad I found you. You allow me to be who I truly am.//Thank you, honey.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm so glad I found you. You allow me to be who I truly am.//Thank you, honey.

Text.SourceString: Not all my tattoos have some deep, profound meaning behind them.
Text.LocalizedString: Not all my tattoos have some deep, profound meaning behind them.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes you just gotta go with the flow, trust your instincts, and get inked.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes you just gotta go with the flow, trust your instincts, and get inked.

Text.SourceString: My hair has been rocking the green look for so long, I wouldn't even know how to answer if you asked about my natural hair color.
Text.LocalizedString: My hair has been rocking the green look for so long, I wouldn't even know how to answer if you asked about my natural hair color.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Charles</> has to take his antihistamine…//I don’t know what else to tell him. It will literally make him feel better.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Charles</> has to take his antihistamine…//I don’t know what else to tell him. It will literally make him feel better.

Text.SourceString: Gotta say, not really a big fan of Spring. It’s just not for me.
Text.LocalizedString: Gotta say, not really a big fan of Spring. It’s just not for me.

Text.SourceString: We do our restocking every Spring… Makes it easier to remember.//Spring…restocking. See?
Text.LocalizedString: We do our restocking every Spring… Makes it easier to remember.//Spring…restocking. See?

Text.SourceString: Have you had your flu vaccine yet?//I recommend getting it every year. Even if the strain changes, at least you'll have some protection.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you had your flu vaccine yet?//I recommend getting it every year. Even if the strain changes, at least you'll have some protection.

Text.SourceString: Most people usually get their flu vaccines in Winter or Spring. That’s when you’re most vulnerable.//I get mine in Fall to prepare for the coming season. Give it a try, see how it feels.
Text.LocalizedString: Most people usually get their flu vaccines in Winter or Spring. That’s when you’re most vulnerable.//I get mine in Fall to prepare for the coming season. Give it a try, see how it feels.

Text.SourceString: The Cherry Blossom Festival was really nice, wasn’t it?//<portrait=normal>I had a lot of fun. I like going to festivals with you, hun
Text.LocalizedString: The Cherry Blossom Festival was really nice, wasn’t it?//<portrait=normal>I had a lot of fun. I like going to festivals with you, hun

Text.SourceString: Don’t worry about <NPCName>Charles</>. He’s in good hands.//<portrait=normal>I've got everything under control. Let me do the worrying for the both of us, cool?
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t worry about <NPCName>Charles</>. He’s in good hands.//<portrait=normal>I've got everything under control. Let me do the worrying for the both of us, cool?

Text.SourceString: Phew, are you sweating as much as I am? This heat is intense!
Text.LocalizedString: Phew, are you sweating as much as I am? This heat is intense!

Text.SourceString: It’s so hot, <PlayerName>$player</>.//It takes me back to my days volunteering in the doctor program.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s so hot, <PlayerName>$player</>.//It takes me back to my days volunteering in the doctor program.

Text.SourceString: Good thing I'm not wearing a full-blown doctor's coat in this heat. Loose clothing all the way.
Text.LocalizedString: Good thing I'm not wearing a full-blown doctor's coat in this heat. Loose clothing all the way.

Text.SourceString: Gotta give your body room to breathe… Not sandals, though.//<portrait=happy>I can’t run in those.
Text.LocalizedString: Gotta give your body room to breathe… Not sandals, though.//<portrait=happy>I can’t run in those.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Charles</> and I always prepare for medical emergencies at the Beach Cleanup Festival… Nothing in particular.//It’s good to have doctors around at big gatherings in case someone gets heatstroke or something like that.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Charles</> and I always prepare for medical emergencies at the Beach Cleanup Festival… Nothing in particular.//It’s good to have doctors around at big gatherings in case someone gets heatstroke or something like that.

Text.SourceString: Will you be entering the swimming contest, hun?
Text.LocalizedString: Will you be entering the swimming contest, hun?

Text.SourceString: I think <NPCName>Sunny</> is going to win. He’s got some stamina… Very fast swimmer.
Text.LocalizedString: I think <NPCName>Sunny</> is going to win. He’s got some stamina… Very fast swimmer.

Text.SourceString: I got this small handheld fan… Oh, so good.//<portrait=normal>Fully automated, battery operated, and all that. You can take it with you in your pocket. The perfect Summer toy.
Text.LocalizedString: I got this small handheld fan… Oh, so good.//<portrait=normal>Fully automated, battery operated, and all that. You can take it with you in your pocket. The perfect Summer toy.

Text.SourceString: I had one, anyway… I don’t have the fan anymore.//Accidentally stepped on it. And nobody sells them here.
Text.LocalizedString: I had one, anyway… I don’t have the fan anymore.//Accidentally stepped on it. And nobody sells them here.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Millie</> used to keep so many melons in the fridge.//<portrait=concerned>That girl... she can go a little overboard when she likes something.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Millie</> used to keep so many melons in the fridge.//<portrait=concerned>That girl... she can go a little overboard when she likes something.

Text.SourceString: Finally, the perfect weather for eating curry.//Curry in Summer is fine, of course, but the heat from inside and out can be too much sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: Finally, the perfect weather for eating curry.//Curry in Summer is fine, of course, but the heat from inside and out can be too much sometimes.

Text.SourceString: I'm so glad the air has cooled down. It's a breath of fresh air, quite literally.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm so glad the air has cooled down. It's a breath of fresh air, quite literally.

Text.SourceString: What is it they say about Fall? Sweater weather?//<portrait=normal>Yeah, I think that’s right.
Text.LocalizedString: What is it they say about Fall? Sweater weather?//<portrait=normal>Yeah, I think that’s right.

Text.SourceString: Are you going to show your crops at the Harvest Festival, hun?//<portrait=happy>You're gonna win this round, I can feel it!
Text.LocalizedString: Are you going to show your crops at the Harvest Festival, hun?//<portrait=happy>You're gonna win this round, I can feel it!

Text.SourceString: I think tonight's dinner is gonna be curry. Seems like the right weather for it.
Text.LocalizedString: I think tonight's dinner is gonna be curry. Seems like the right weather for it.

Text.SourceString: Do you ever think about how lucky we are to have Winter?//I'd take layering up in the cold over constantly sweating in the heat any day.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you ever think about how lucky we are to have Winter?//I'd take layering up in the cold over constantly sweating in the heat any day.

Text.SourceString: Winter is usually our busiest season. People tend to get sick more often, which is why I prefer getting my flu shot in Fall.//It's all about preparation, <PlayerName>$Player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter is usually our busiest season. People tend to get sick more often, which is why I prefer getting my flu shot in Fall.//It's all about preparation, <PlayerName>$Player</>.

Text.SourceString: We've stocked up on plenty of cold medicine for this season.//The weather is dry and cold, just the way those viruses like it.
Text.LocalizedString: We've stocked up on plenty of cold medicine for this season.//The weather is dry and cold, just the way those viruses like it.

Text.SourceString: Here we go. It’s Winter. I need to make sure I stay healthy all season.
Text.LocalizedString: Here we go. It’s Winter. I need to make sure I stay healthy all season.

Text.SourceString: Finally, the perfect weather for curry. Now <Italic>this</> is what Winter is all about.//It's like the ultimate comfort food season.
Text.LocalizedString: Finally, the perfect weather for curry. Now <Italic>this</> is what Winter is all about.//It's like the ultimate comfort food season.

Text.SourceString: The other day, I was at the store looking for some kale for my midday snack, but guess what? <NPCName>Sam</> didn't have any. Bummer!
Text.LocalizedString: The other day, I was at the store looking for some kale for my midday snack, but guess what? <NPCName>Sam</> didn't have any. Bummer!

Text.SourceString: I guess it's not kale season anymore. Time to find another leafy green to munch on.
Text.LocalizedString: I guess it's not kale season anymore. Time to find another leafy green to munch on.

Text.SourceString: Spring just arrived, and poor <NPCName>Charles</> can't stop sneezing his nose off.//<portrait=annoyed>It's a bit worrisome, you know? I hope he finds some relief soon.
Text.LocalizedString: Spring just arrived, and poor <NPCName>Charles</> can't stop sneezing his nose off.//<portrait=annoyed>It's a bit worrisome, you know? I hope he finds some relief soon.

Text.SourceString: I took a walk by the lake the other day and saw so many colorful flowers.//What a season!
Text.LocalizedString: I took a walk by the lake the other day and saw so many colorful flowers.//What a season!

Text.SourceString: There are so many coconuts at the beach right now. It's like a coconut paradise out there.
Text.LocalizedString: There are so many coconuts at the beach right now. It's like a coconut paradise out there.

Text.SourceString: We’re cleaning up the beach soon.
Text.LocalizedString: We’re cleaning up the beach soon.

Text.SourceString: Good thing the beach cleanup starts at 11 am.//<portrait=happy>It gives me a bit of time in the morning to stop by the clinic and pick up some stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: Good thing the beach cleanup starts at 11 am.//<portrait=happy>It gives me a bit of time in the morning to stop by the clinic and pick up some stuff.

Text.SourceString: Hun!!! We should go mushroom foraging sometime.//I've heard black trumpets and matsutakes are sprouting near the school!
Text.LocalizedString: Hun!!! We should go mushroom foraging sometime.//I've heard black trumpets and matsutakes are sprouting near the school!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Dinda</> told me all about it. She's quite the foraging expert
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Dinda</> told me all about it. She's quite the foraging expert

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Millie</> has a lizard that only comes out of hiding when she’s home.//<portrait=happy>Cute little thing.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Millie</> has a lizard that only comes out of hiding when she’s home.//<portrait=happy>Cute little thing.

Text.SourceString: She named the lizard Tin. What a fun name…
Text.LocalizedString: She named the lizard Tin. What a fun name…

Text.SourceString: With the weather getting colder, it's like people are hibernating or something.//<portrait=annoyed>Have you noticed? Streets are practically empty these days
Text.LocalizedString: With the weather getting colder, it's like people are hibernating or something.//<portrait=annoyed>Have you noticed? Streets are practically empty these days

Text.SourceString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.

Text.SourceString: I thought I’d have more time to read this Winter, but right now I’m more swamped than ever.
Text.LocalizedString: I thought I’d have more time to read this Winter, but right now I’m more swamped than ever.

Text.SourceString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.

Text.SourceString: The rain doesn’t change anything, I think…//<portrait=annoyed>But it does slow life down a little.
Text.LocalizedString: The rain doesn’t change anything, I think…//<portrait=annoyed>But it does slow life down a little.

Text.SourceString: I guess it gives us more time for cuddling
Text.LocalizedString: I guess it gives us more time for cuddling

Text.SourceString: I wish I could have slept in today. It’s the perfect weather for waking up late and going to bed early.//Join me, hun?
Text.LocalizedString: I wish I could have slept in today. It’s the perfect weather for waking up late and going to bed early.//Join me, hun?

Text.SourceString: I wish I could have slept in today. It’s the perfect weather for waking up late and going to bed early.//Join me, hun?
Text.LocalizedString: I wish I could have slept in today. It’s the perfect weather for waking up late and going to bed early.//Join me, hun?

Text.SourceString: The rain doesn’t change anything, I think…//<portrait=annoyed>But it does slow life down a little.
Text.LocalizedString: The rain doesn’t change anything, I think…//<portrait=annoyed>But it does slow life down a little.

Text.SourceString: I guess it gives us more time for cuddling
Text.LocalizedString: I guess it gives us more time for cuddling

Text.SourceString: I’m trying to get more people to go out and garden.//It’s an easy way to get daily exercise.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m trying to get more people to go out and garden.//It’s an easy way to get daily exercise.

Text.SourceString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.

Text.SourceString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh gosh, piping hot curry would be perfect right now.

Text.SourceString: Is it snowing again or something?
Text.LocalizedString: Is it snowing again or something?

Text.SourceString: You’d think it would’ve stopped by now.
Text.LocalizedString: You’d think it would’ve stopped by now.

Text.SourceString: I could use one of those thick knitted blankets right now. Humph…
Text.LocalizedString: I could use one of those thick knitted blankets right now. Humph…

Text.SourceString: One of my favorite things to do after work is to come here and read medical journals until the sun sets.//It's my way of keeping up with the latest medical advancements.
Text.LocalizedString: One of my favorite things to do after work is to come here and read medical journals until the sun sets.//It's my way of keeping up with the latest medical advancements.

Text.SourceString: I’m subscribed to four journals, and I've even been published in a few.//Mostly articles about interesting medical cases I encountered during my travels.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m subscribed to four journals, and I've even been published in a few.//Mostly articles about interesting medical cases I encountered during my travels.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, all we need is a little peace and quiet, right?//Just a moment to unwind and clear our minds.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, all we need is a little peace and quiet, right?//Just a moment to unwind and clear our minds.

Text.SourceString: Even though the clinic is closed on Sundays, <NPCName>Charles</> and I are always ready for emergencies.//So don't worry, we've got you covered.
Text.LocalizedString: Even though the clinic is closed on Sundays, <NPCName>Charles</> and I are always ready for emergencies.//So don't worry, we've got you covered.

Text.SourceString: I like my scrubs. They’re comfortable and easy to clean.//But I should wear my white coat once in a while…//<portrait=happy>Change things up a bit.
Text.LocalizedString: I like my scrubs. They’re comfortable and easy to clean.//But I should wear my white coat once in a while…//<portrait=happy>Change things up a bit.

Text.SourceString: You know, like <NPCName>Charles</>. He looks good in his coat.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, like <NPCName>Charles</>. He looks good in his coat.

Text.SourceString: Whenever I can, I try to squeeze in some dancing. It's like an instant mood-booster.//<portrait=happy>Hey, we should go dancing together sometime.
Text.LocalizedString: Whenever I can, I try to squeeze in some dancing. It's like an instant mood-booster.//<portrait=happy>Hey, we should go dancing together sometime.

Text.SourceString: I'll be honest, I'm not the greatest dancer out there. But as long as I'm not hurting anyone and it makes me feel good, who really cares?
Text.LocalizedString: I'll be honest, I'm not the greatest dancer out there. But as long as I'm not hurting anyone and it makes me feel good, who really cares?

Text.SourceString: I may have had one too many cups of punch. I’m going to call it a night.
Text.LocalizedString: I may have had one too many cups of punch. I’m going to call it a night.

Text.SourceString: I was going to practice some volleyball earlier, but there was nobody outside.//So I decided to chill here instead.
Text.LocalizedString: I was going to practice some volleyball earlier, but there was nobody outside.//So I decided to chill here instead.

Text.SourceString: Wah...I'm seriously craving some seafood today.//Let's see what <NPCName>Jim</> is cooking up. His dishes are always spot on.
Text.LocalizedString: Wah...I'm seriously craving some seafood today.//Let's see what <NPCName>Jim</> is cooking up. His dishes are always spot on.

Text.SourceString: Phew! The sun is really blazing today, huh?//I think I’ll enjoy the beach from inside here.
Text.LocalizedString: Phew! The sun is really blazing today, huh?//I think I’ll enjoy the beach from inside here.

Text.SourceString: I'm grabbing some extra stuff for the house.//<portrait=happy>Should we also grab more bread, hun? Or cookies? They smell amazing!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm grabbing some extra stuff for the house.//<portrait=happy>Should we also grab more bread, hun? Or cookies? They smell amazing!

Text.SourceString: The radishes here are incredibly crunchy and great for pickling.
Text.LocalizedString: The radishes here are incredibly crunchy and great for pickling.

Text.SourceString: The radishes here are incredibly crunchy and great for pickling.
Text.LocalizedString: The radishes here are incredibly crunchy and great for pickling.

Text.SourceString: The eggplants here make incredible pickles.
Text.LocalizedString: The eggplants here make incredible pickles.

Text.SourceString: The eggplants here make incredible pickles.
Text.LocalizedString: The eggplants here make incredible pickles.

Text.SourceString: I think I got a bit too much sun at the beach yesterday.//Oops! Time to lather on some aloe vera.
Text.LocalizedString: I think I got a bit too much sun at the beach yesterday.//Oops! Time to lather on some aloe vera.

Text.SourceString: Don’t overwork yourself, hun. I don’t wanna see you in the clinic.
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t overwork yourself, hun. I don’t wanna see you in the clinic.

Text.SourceString: The heat can be exhausting. Please be careful.
Text.LocalizedString: The heat can be exhausting. Please be careful.

Text.SourceString: Want to play pool with me? I could use a win. Heh, heh!
Text.LocalizedString: Want to play pool with me? I could use a win. Heh, heh!

Text.SourceString: Have you eaten, <PlayerName>$player</>? Please make sure you eat meals on time, okay?//Something healthy to boost your immune system, maybe.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you eaten, <PlayerName>$player</>? Please make sure you eat meals on time, okay?//Something healthy to boost your immune system, maybe.

Text.SourceString: I worry about you…
Text.LocalizedString: I worry about you…

Text.SourceString: You look spiffy today, <PlayerName>$player</>!//<portrait=happy>You could pass as a Winter decoration.
Text.LocalizedString: You look spiffy today, <PlayerName>$player</>!//<portrait=happy>You could pass as a Winter decoration.

Text.SourceString: Oh my! I meant you look nice… Nice, nice, nice.//<portrait=happy>You don’t look bad or anything.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh my! I meant you look nice… Nice, nice, nice.//<portrait=happy>You don’t look bad or anything.

Text.SourceString: I'm not giving up on mastering the art of making curry.//One day, mark my words, I'll whip up the best curry on this whole island. They'll call me the Curry Master!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not giving up on mastering the art of making curry.//One day, mark my words, I'll whip up the best curry on this whole island. They'll call me the Curry Master!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Frank</> currently holds the title… He’s a great cook, isn’t he? Humph. Hard to beat.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Frank</> currently holds the title… He’s a great cook, isn’t he? Humph. Hard to beat.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes it feels a little strange calling myself a doctor. I mean, deep down, I don't really feel like one.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes it feels a little strange calling myself a doctor. I mean, deep down, I don't really feel like one.

Text.SourceString: In my head, doctors are all serious and stuff.//Whatever that means.
Text.LocalizedString: In my head, doctors are all serious and stuff.//Whatever that means.

Text.SourceString: I feel so close to you… I can smell you from here.
Text.LocalizedString: I feel so close to you… I can smell you from here.

Text.SourceString: It’s nice… You smell really nice.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s nice… You smell really nice.

Text.SourceString: Just finished submitting my billing for the week.
Text.LocalizedString: Just finished submitting my billing for the week.

Text.SourceString: Feels good to get that paperwork done, even if it's not the most exciting task.
Text.LocalizedString: Feels good to get that paperwork done, even if it's not the most exciting task.

Text.SourceString: I'm here to pick up some new reading material. Already finished everything I had.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm here to pick up some new reading material. Already finished everything I had.

Text.SourceString: As soon as Summer hits, I’m wearing my bikini all the time.//<portrait=happy>I’m throwing myself at the beach every single day. Can’t wait!
Text.LocalizedString: As soon as Summer hits, I’m wearing my bikini all the time.//<portrait=happy>I’m throwing myself at the beach every single day. Can’t wait!

Text.SourceString: I got this jacket back when I was in Tangi working with the Universal Doctors.//Feel it! Good quality, right? It was really cheap too.
Text.LocalizedString: I got this jacket back when I was in Tangi working with the Universal Doctors.//Feel it! Good quality, right? It was really cheap too.

Text.SourceString: The jacket is really warm. You’d be surprised!
Text.LocalizedString: The jacket is really warm. You’d be surprised!

Text.SourceString: Spring here isn’t cold. No need to wear a thick jacket anymore.//<portrait=happy>I can move faster now!
Text.LocalizedString: Spring here isn’t cold. No need to wear a thick jacket anymore.//<portrait=happy>I can move faster now!

Text.SourceString: Normally, Spring is when I'd go to medical conferences.//But these days, I prefer attending them online. Can't beat the convenience.
Text.LocalizedString: Normally, Spring is when I'd go to medical conferences.//But these days, I prefer attending them online. Can't beat the convenience.

Text.SourceString: The conferences have free activities like scuba diving, tours, wine tastings… Yeah, It was fun.//Well, the ones I used to go to anyway.
Text.LocalizedString: The conferences have free activities like scuba diving, tours, wine tastings… Yeah, It was fun.//Well, the ones I used to go to anyway.

Text.SourceString: I wonder what kind of medical conferences they've got lined up for this upcoming Spring. Might be worth checking out!
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder what kind of medical conferences they've got lined up for this upcoming Spring. Might be worth checking out!
